/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 放d殺人犯過來, 跟住就話香港冇引渡條例, 屈返香港通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"340912aa3fe6546a66c2f5e4c8939c414054bace","tid":1157194,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:03:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/awang0727/1411833963-2258299323.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fawang0727%2F1411833963-2258299323.jpg&h=892beddb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"30af7aae19fc659945593d9d271ebfbbeb1ad529","tid":1157194,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T11:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ef9de0834584aa423a9b0e72c02dd1a7eca3792","tid":1157194,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T14:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}